Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.12,0:00:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情提要\N{\fs12}Previously on The Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.24,0:00:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\fs12}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你想要的\N{\fs12}This is what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想当爸爸吗\N{\fs12}Do you want to be a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈的订婚戒指还在你那儿吗\N{\fs12}You still have mum's engagement ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给我吗\N{\fs12}I'd like to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,比起婚姻  我们面前有更大的\N{\fs12}We have a much bigger decision in front of us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 决定要做  - 我不  如果你不想嫁给我  我不在乎\N{\fs12}- then marriage. - I don't... I don't care if you don't want to marry me uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的  我只是\N{\fs12}It's alright, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我准备好要做一个父亲了\N{\fs12}I know that I'm ready to be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,关于露露的事儿  我  呃\N{\fs12}About lulu, I'm ... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我特别为你高兴\N{\fs12}I'm happy as hell for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一切事情的发展\N{\fs12}I'm just very pleased,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,都让我感到非常开心\N{\fs12}by the way everything's turning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哈西看起来很生气\N{\fs12}Hassey looks pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他本来看起来就这样\N{\fs12}No, it's just the way he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你们亲眼看看\N{\fs12}Wanted you to see this for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,流浪者  非法占有者  毒贩  他们还都在这里\N{\fs12}Bums, squatters, drug peddlers, they're all still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我将在下周开展200个单位的开发\N{\fs12}Now, I'm breaking ground on a 200 unit development next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你答应过我你会处理这件事的\N{\fs12}You promised me you were gonna take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我已经和匹兹堡警察局谈过两次了\N{\fs12}I know, and I've spoken to the Pittsburgh Police Department twice already--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那就再跟他们谈\N{\fs12}Well, speak to them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我雇你的公司是因为你们可以对付那帮臭警察\N{\fs12}I mean, the reason I hired your firm is you represent the damn cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明白这个问题\N{\fs12}We understand the problem, Ron--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是想要你明白这个问题  伯顿\N{\fs12}I don't want you to understand the problem, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是希望你可以解决它\N{\fs12}I want you to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就去找市政厅的关系  好吗\N{\fs12}We'll go down and see our people at the city, right now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是负责人\N{\fs12}Who's in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是这里的负责人\N{\fs12}Who's the officer in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  女士  在这里\N{\fs12}Hey, lady! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷  爷爷\N{\fs12}Gramps! Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我  伙计\N{\fs12}Get off me, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,劳里·绍尔特  社会服务中心  我接到了电话\N{\fs12}Laurie Solt, Social Services. I got a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  这孩子和他祖父就住在这里\N{\fs12}Yeah, this kid and his grandpa were living here unlamully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是在救护车里的那个吗\N{\fs12}That the grandfather in the ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  他们把我们赶出房子之后  他就晕过去了\N{\fs12}Yeah! After they threw us out of our house, he collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他生病了\N{\fs12}He's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  现在的地产所有者希望他们可以离开\N{\fs12}Hey, the rightful owners wanted them evicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会知道他们要把你祖父带到哪里去的\N{\fs12}We'll find out where they're taking your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好  你好吗\N{\fs12}Good afternoon. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不错  - 挺好\N{\fs12}- Fine. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唐尼·隆戈\N{\fs12}This is Donnie Longo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的公司今天早上把他赶出了家\N{\fs12}Your firm threw him out of his home this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和这些大多数剩下的人一样\N{\fs12}along with most of the rest of these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,唐尼\N{\fs12}Donnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的委托人\N{\fs12}He's your client.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,收容所听证会  下午2点\N{\fs12}Shelter hearing, 2 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,露露分配给我的案子\N{\fs12}Lulu assigns my cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我和露露谈过了  她说他是你的案子\N{\fs12}I talked to Lulu. She said he's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的烂摊子  把他解决完\N{\fs12}lt's your mess. Help clean it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,各位  请坐下来安静一下\N{\fs12}Everybody, please, keep it down and have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我一会就回来\N{\fs12}I'll be with you in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  这只是一张驴子的照片\N{\fs12}You see, this is just a picture of a donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我没用处\N{\fs12}This doesn't help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,各位  请大家注意一下好吗\N{\fs12}Uh, everyone, could I have your attention, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等一下\N{\fs12}Please, just a for minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在竭尽全力寻找你们每个人都可以住的的地方\N{\fs12}We're doing everything we can to find each of you a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过需要一些时间  好吗  对此我感到很抱歉\N{\fs12}lt's just gonna take some time, okay? I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当你们填写完了全部资料  如果有任何问题\N{\fs12}When you finish all of your paperwork, if you have any questions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,或者有什么我可以帮你们的话  就告诉我\N{\fs12}or if there's anything I can do for you, then Iet me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉你的上衣\N{\fs12}Take off your top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  非常感谢\N{\fs12}Thank you. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那位女士是什么意思\N{\fs12}What did that lady mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你的烂摊子\N{\fs12}''Your mess.''
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么事\N{\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  她说的好像是你把所有人都赶出去了\N{\fs12}Well, she said it like you were the guy who threw everybody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fs12}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但她就是那样说的\N{\fs12}But she said it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿没什么信息\N{\fs12}There's not a lot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有遇到过麻烦\N{\fs12}I never been in any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你上学吗\N{\fs12}You go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  埃文代尔高中\N{\fs12}Yeah. Avondale High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母呢\N{\fs12}How about your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经死了  那时候我才差不多四岁  听着\N{\fs12}They died when I was, like, four. Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎我们住在哪里  我只想和爷爷在一起  好吗\N{\fs12}I don't care where we live, I just want to be with Gramps, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想办法帮助你\N{\fs12}I'm trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  但那女人说得好像是你把我们赶出去了\N{\fs12}Well, that lady kinda made it sound like you threw us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 唐尼·隆戈  - 是我\N{\fs12}-- Donnie Longo? --Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是路易莎·阿切尔  我将和你祖父一起工作\N{\fs12}I'm Louisa Archer. I'll be working with your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要去医院看他  你想不想要搭便车\N{\fs12}I'm going to see him at the hospital now if you want a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该在场\N{\fs12}You should be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比  福克斯下台后\N{\fs12}Abby, with Fox stepping down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,市议会就没有真正的自由主义了\N{\fs12}there's not one true liberal voice left on the City Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一个人真正了解我们的城市发生了什么\N{\fs12}Not one person who truly understands what's happening in our city,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,穷人发生了什么\N{\fs12}with our poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,上次竞选时  你就淘汰了\N{\fs12}Last time you ran, you got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我在选举中失败了 多了不起啊\N{\fs12}I lost an election. Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你获得了百分之四的选票\N{\fs12}You got four percent of the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我那时候才29\N{\fs12}I was 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人比我了解法律\N{\fs12}No one has my understanding of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有人也没有人像我一样和弱势群体合作过\N{\fs12}Or my track record of working with the under-privileged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但同样也没有相关机构记录过\N{\fs12}No one has your track record with the authorities either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会记得那些事情\N{\fs12}Who remembers that stum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要竞选的话 你的对手会记起来的\N{\fs12}Your opponents will, if you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我准备为自己辩护\N{\fs12}So I'm prepared to defend myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比  拜托\N{\fs12}Abby, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不再管理这个地方了  我有时间了\N{\fs12}Now that I don't run this place anymore, I have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经认识很久了  阿尔文  所以我要告诉你\N{\fs12}We've known each other a long time, Alvin, so I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我倾向于  不要\N{\fs12}I'm leaning toward a... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两位是索尔特女士派来的吗\N{\fs12}You two gentlemen sent here by Ms. Solt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个好看的老女人\N{\fs12}The good-looking older broad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么不来我办公室呢\N{\fs12}Why don't you guys come on in my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我想你需要一个住处\N{\fs12}So, I'm assuming you need a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  一个不错的地方\N{\fs12}Yeah. Someplace nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是现在几乎是冬天了  所有好的避难所都满了\N{\fs12}Well, the problem is it's almost winter, so all the good shelters are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那些不是的  他们的服务对象是未成年人和未婚妈妈\N{\fs12}Those that aren't, cater to juveniles, unwed mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,休利特公寓怎么样\N{\fs12}What about the Hewlett House?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的一个家伙说那里很不错\N{\fs12}A guy I know who got in there says it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是单单去休利特公寓就好了  你得断毒断酒\N{\fs12}You don't just walk into the Hewlett House. You have to be sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须在住进去两周内找到工作\N{\fs12}You have to have a job within two weeks of residency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你还需要付一些房租\N{\fs12}You're required to pay some rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那他为什么要先走\N{\fs12}So why does he get to go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  等一下  您为什么不坐下来呢?\N{\fs12}I'll be with you in a minute, sir. Why don't you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在周末打扫停车场  一周60英镑\N{\fs12}I sweep parking lots on weekends, make 60 a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经五个月没有犯瘾了\N{\fs12}And I've been clean for five months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不填一份申请表  我来看看我能做些什么\N{\fs12}Why don't you fill out an application, and I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  谢谢你  真的非常感谢你\N{\fs12}Oh, thank you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  超级流浪汉\N{\fs12}Yeah! Super Bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要给我一份休利特公寓的表格吗\N{\fs12}You gonna give me one of those Hewlett House forms, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不是吧\N{\fs12}Didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,全名\N{\fs12}Full name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,雷·施米尔  我的朋友们叫我鲁弗斯\N{\fs12}Ray Schmiel. My friends call me Rufus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,最高学历  雷\N{\fs12}Highest level of education, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你参加一个由政府资助的职业项目\N{\fs12}I was gonna try and get you into a county-sponsored vocational program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  只要给我找到一个地方像杰拉尔德一样就好了\N{\fs12}Well, just find me a place like Gerald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要清醒一点  你必须要有一份工作\N{\fs12}You have to be sober. You have to have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  最高学历\N{\fs12}So... highest level of education?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哈佛\N{\fs12}Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,施米尔先生  你在浪费时间\N{\fs12}You're wasting my time, Mr. Schmiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  奥尔德里奇高中\N{\fs12}All right. Aldrich High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的最高学历\N{\fs12}My highest level of education.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  你什么时候毕业\N{\fs12}Yeah? When did you graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,54年\N{\fs12}'54.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识罗伯特·马斯特森吗\N{\fs12}Did you know a Robert Masterson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是谁  - 我父亲\N{\fs12}-- Who's that? -- My dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍比·马斯特森\N{\fs12}Bobby Masterson!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然知道他\N{\fs12}Sure I knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好人啊  他现在怎么样了\N{\fs12}Great guy. How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他去世了\N{\fs12}He passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  太可惜了\N{\fs12}Aw. Damn shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在店里面一起工作了四年\N{\fs12}We were in shop together all four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我放在那里因为我不是一个非常好的学生  你知道的\N{\fs12}They put me in there because I'm not a very good student, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你父亲  他真的很好\N{\fs12}But your dad? Oh, he was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,高三时获得最佳项目奖\N{\fs12}Won Best Project, senior year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,做了一个猪一样形状的砧板\N{\fs12}Made a cutting board shaped like a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的父亲吗  - 是的  他很有才华\N{\fs12}-- My dad? -- Yeah. He was talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈  世界真小啊  伙计  世界真小\N{\fs12}Ha ha! Small world, man. Small world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  唐尼\N{\fs12}Hey, Donnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏  像往常一样\N{\fs12}Oh, the ticker, like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,疼不疼\N{\fs12}Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  有一点\N{\fs12}It did, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在好多了\N{\fs12}I feel good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,唐尼  医生问我药的事了\N{\fs12}Hey, Donnie, the doc asked me about my pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得了\N{\fs12}I can never remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他你都知道  所以\N{\fs12}I told him you know 'em all, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能在楼下大厅\N{\fs12}He's probably down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,去告诉他  好吗\N{\fs12}Go tell him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 好孩子\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,隆戈先生  我是匹兹堡法律服务部的路易莎·阿切尔\N{\fs12}Mr. Longo, I'm Louisa Archer from Legal Services of Pittsburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是律师\N{\fs12}You a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  如果你愿意  我可以在唐尼的收容所听证会上帮忙\N{\fs12}Yes, and if you want, I can help you with Donnie's shelter hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,收容所听证会\N{\fs12}Shelter hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,社会服务有点担心你照顾唐尼的能力\N{\fs12}Well, Social Services is concerned about your ability to care for Donnie,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到你的健康和  现在你没有家了\N{\fs12}considering your health and...well, now the fact that you have no home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,警察说我不能再待在那里了\N{\fs12}The cops said I couldn't stay there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,业主希望您可以离开\N{\fs12}The owner wanted you evicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是现在\N{\fs12}Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我从65年就住在那儿了\N{\fs12}I've been there since '65.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你从1965年起就住在那栋房子里了吗\N{\fs12}You've been living in that house since 1965?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啊  - 非法占用吗\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - Squatting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的  是租房  至少有一段时间是的\N{\fs12}No, renting. At least for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂你的意思  你从谁那里租的\N{\fs12}I'm not following you. Who were you renting from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我不记得了  某个家庭吧\N{\fs12}Oh, I don't remember. Some family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拥有这块土地上所有的房子\N{\fs12}They owned all the homes on the lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就不再租房了\N{\fs12}And then you stopped renting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再支付费用了\N{\fs12}I stopped paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这些房子本来就不太好\N{\fs12}Well, the houses weren't too good to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而那个家庭  却让它们散架了\N{\fs12}and that family, they just let them fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我停止了支付房租\N{\fs12}So I stopped paying rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么时候\N{\fs12}And when was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  大约在79年\N{\fs12}Oh, around '79.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你就一直住在那里\N{\fs12}And you just kept living there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,70年代钢铁厂倒闭后  我找不到工作\N{\fs12}When the steel mills shut down in the seventies, I couldn't find work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我就生病了\N{\fs12}Then I got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不打算放弃一个免费的住所\N{\fs12}I wasn't about to give up a free home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我和唐尼会怎么样\N{\fs12}What's gonna happen to me and Donnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会主张违法占有吧\N{\fs12}You're not gonna argue adverse possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果隆戈先生可以证明他一直住在那里的话\N{\fs12}lf Mr. Longo can prove he's been living on that property
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,21年没有支付租金\N{\fs12}without paying rent, for 21 years--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么证明这一点\N{\fs12}How you gonna prove this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果他说的是真的  那产权就是他的\N{\fs12}Well, if what he's saying is true, the property belongs to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你是在告诉我  如果有人在别人的房子里住得够久的话\N{\fs12}So you're telling me that if someone lives on someone else's property long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,房子就是他们的了\N{\fs12}it just becomes theirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他连续21年住在这里  而业主却什么也没有做\N{\fs12}lf he lives on it for 21 consecutive years and the owner does nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我他是错的\N{\fs12}Tell me he's wrong about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  当务之急是要朗格先生证实他说的话\N{\fs12}Well, the burden will be on Mr. Longo to prove his claim,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但既然你现在是合法所有人  这在法庭上很有发言权\N{\fs12}but since you're currently the legal owner, that'll sit well in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,合法所有人\N{\fs12}Currently the legal owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我从县里光明正大地把这处房产买了下来\N{\fs12}I bought this property fair and square from the county.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在拍卖会上买的  但要付所有的留置权和索赔权\N{\fs12}You bought it at auction, subject to all liens and claims,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这就是索赔\N{\fs12}and this is a claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哈西先生  他们只有一个不靠谱的老头说的话\N{\fs12}Mr. Hassey, all they have is the word of an unreliable old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,罗恩  我们需要你签字\N{\fs12}Ron? We need you to sign for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个项目每天都被延迟  我就赔钱  你明白吗\N{\fs12}And every day this project is delayed, I lose money. You understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能有点冲突\N{\fs12}I may have a conflict here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会呢\N{\fs12}How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表隆戈先生的孙子出席了他在收容所的听证会\N{\fs12}I'm representing Mr. Longo's grandson at his shelter hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,又是LSP律所\N{\fs12}LSP again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我仍然可以为那位委托人工作  露露还没有提交任何文件\N{\fs12}Well, I can still work for the client. Lulu hasn't filed anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯  她会的  我会和她谈谈的\N{\fs12}-- Well, she will. -- I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你能否说服她\N{\fs12}See if you can talk some sense into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  你的生日快到了\N{\fs12}Now, listen, uh, your birthday's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不跟香农和我在纳马林过个周末呢\N{\fs12}Why don't you and Shannon and l spend a weekend at Namacolin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,泡个温泉  做个按摩  放松一下\N{\fs12}Hit a spa, get a massage. You know, relax a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 按摩吗  - 是啊\N{\fs12}-- A massage? -- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有那种裹泥的东西  不管你叫它什么\N{\fs12}They've got that mud-wrapping thing, whatever you call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,应该效果不错的\N{\fs12}lt's supposed to work pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我看看我的日程安排\N{\fs12}Well, I'll check my schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对你有好处的\N{\fs12}Be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在隆戈康复后  天主教慈善机构有一个机构\N{\fs12}Upon Mr. Longo's recovery, Catholic Charities has a facility
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,目的是让无家可归的家庭团聚\N{\fs12}whose goal is to keep homeless families together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阿彻尔女士  这是专为单身母亲和她们的孩子设计的\N{\fs12}Ms. Archer, that facility is designed for single mothers and their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  但他们的章程里没有否认\N{\fs12}Right, but there's nothing in their charter that denies--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,索尔特女士  社会服务的立场是什么呢\N{\fs12}Ms. Solt, what is Social Services' position?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,唐尼·隆戈在照顾一个生病的成年人时  一直生活在可怕的环境中\N{\fs12}Donnie Longo has lived in horrible conditions while caring for a sick adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在此期间  他半正规地就读于学校\N{\fs12}During that time, he's attended school on a semi-regular basis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也没惹麻烦\N{\fs12}and kept out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想想如果把他放在合适的环境里  他会做什么\N{\fs12}lmagine what he'd do if placed in the proper environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,唐尼做得好是因为他祖父  而不是他\N{\fs12}Donnie did well because of his grandfather, not in spite of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有理由把他们分开\N{\fs12}There's no reason to keep them separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\fs12}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你建议他和他祖父一起住在医院吗\N{\fs12}Do you suggest he live in the hospital with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我建议隆戈先生康复后\N{\fs12}No, I suggest when Mr. Longo recovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些都是为了找到这两个人可以住在一起的地方\N{\fs12}all emorts be made to find a facility where these two can live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧  但与此同时  他需要一个住的地方\N{\fs12}Possibly. But in the meantime, he needs some place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我把唐纳德安置在阿勒格尼男孩收容所\N{\fs12}So, I'm placing Donald in the Allegheny Boys Shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,直到找到合适的寄养家庭\N{\fs12}until a suitable foster family can be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果隆戈先生那时候\N{\fs12}lf the time comes where Mr. Longo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有能力为他的孙子提供足够的照顾\N{\fs12}is able to provide adequate care for his grandson,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会重新讨论这个问题\N{\fs12}we will revisit this issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,阿勒格尼男孩收容所\N{\fs12}Allegheny Boys Shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是那么糟糕\N{\fs12}lt's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等  我爷爷怎么样  我的意思是\N{\fs12}Wait. What about Gramps? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要照顾他  不然他会死在那里的\N{\fs12}I need to take care of him. He'll die in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有医生会照顾你的祖父\N{\fs12}There are doctors that can take care of your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道什么时候给他吃药\N{\fs12}But I know when to give him his pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道该往他的果汁里放多少水  他的胃就不会痛了\N{\fs12}I know how much water to put in his juice so his stomach won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要和他在一起  你得让我跟他回去\N{\fs12}I need to be with him. You need to get me back with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不行  唐尼\N{\fs12}lt's not gonna happen right now, Donnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我走吧  唐尼  我们应该离开了\N{\fs12}Come on, Donnie. We should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过你会让我们在一起的\N{\fs12}You said you'd keep us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  如果拉尔夫·隆戈有一个家或一些钱\N{\fs12}Now, if Ralph Longo had a home or some money,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他是可以留在他的孙子身边的\N{\fs12}he could stay with his grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,争论违法占用权  你不可能胜诉\N{\fs12}You're not gonna win on adverse possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是占居者这么说就行的\N{\fs12}not based on the word of an illegal squatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  好吧\N{\fs12}Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回医院了\N{\fs12}I gotta get back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们今晚再谈\N{\fs12}All right, we'll talk about it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Yeah, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要\N{\fs12}I'm gonna have the--the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,西冷牛排  七分熟\N{\fs12}the New York Strip, medium well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克丹尼\N{\fs12}and a Jack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,占边威士忌\N{\fs12}Jim Beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不会给你买酒的\N{\fs12}No, I'm not buying you alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲也很固执\N{\fs12}Your old man was stubborn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,固执\N{\fs12}Stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直认为他是  呃\N{\fs12}I always thought of him as, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道    也许说是平庸吧\N{\fs12}I don't know... indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的\N{\fs12}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以成为任何他想成为的人\N{\fs12}He was a real mule when he wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次  我们有位老师  特伯先生\N{\fs12}This one time, we had this teacher, Mr. Turbain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,特伯一直在欺负这个孩子 安迪·布劳纳  因为他结结巴巴的\N{\fs12}Turbain was always picking on this kid, Andy Blauner, because he stuttered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他布布布 布劳纳\N{\fs12}Called him B-B-B-Blauner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来像个了不起的老师啊\N{\fs12}Sounds like a great teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以有一天  在上课前\N{\fs12}So one day, before class,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,布劳纳在黑板上写了\N{\fs12}Blauner wrote on the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,特伯是一个胖胖胖胖  胖屁股\N{\fs12}''Turbain is a f-f-f-f-fat ass.''
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  写了五次\N{\fs12}You know, like with five ''F''s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以特伯进来的时候  他非常生气\N{\fs12}So Turbain comes in, and he blows his top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,然后拿出了他的戒尺  抓住了布劳纳\N{\fs12}And he takes out his paddle, and he grabs Blauner,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,把他从座位上推开  推到桌子上去\N{\fs12}and he yanks him out of his seat and bends him over the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就在他要被打晕的时候\N{\fs12}And just about when he's gonna get whacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的老爸跳起来说\N{\fs12}your old man jumps up and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是我干的  胖胖胖胖  胖屁股\N{\fs12}''l did it, f-f-f-fat ass.''
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑吧\N{\fs12}You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我能跟你谈一会儿吗\N{\fs12}Alvin. Can I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\fs12}Be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不能和他呆在一起  为什么不能\N{\fs12}-- You can't stay in here with him. -- Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他的外表  说实话  还有他身上的臭味\N{\fs12}His appearance. And, frankly, his stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么  法西斯份子吗\N{\fs12}What are you, a fascist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我不知道那是什么意思  但我不能从酒吧里见到他\N{\fs12}Look, I don't know what that means, but I can smell him from the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  得了吧  杰瑞  饶了他吧\N{\fs12}Oh, come on, Jerry, cut the guy a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  你  - 我们哪儿也不去\N{\fs12}- Alvin, you-- - We're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  伙计  我快死了\N{\fs12}Hey, man, I'm dying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我得喝一杯\N{\fs12}I gotta have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一杯  就一杯\N{\fs12}One, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你在那里生活的那些年里没有支付租金\N{\fs12}So all those years that you lived there without paying rent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,法律称这是对真正的财产所有者的不利生活\N{\fs12}the law calls that ''living adversely'' to the true property owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,生活不利\N{\fs12}Living adversely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 那是什么意思\N{\fs12}- Right. - What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,根据定义  它意味着你住在那里\N{\fs12}Well, by definition it means that you lived there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,以一种开放的  连续的  敌对的方式\N{\fs12}in an open, continuous, and hostile manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不  我从来没有对任何人怀有敌意\N{\fs12}Oh, no, I was never hostile to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这只是一个定义\N{\fs12}No, it's just a definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是你要知道  你在那里住得够久了\N{\fs12}What's important for you to know is that you lived there long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,久得足以声称产权是你的\N{\fs12}to claim that the property is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那房子是我的了吗\N{\fs12}The house is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我们还得让法院同意\N{\fs12}Well, we'd have to get the court to agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想诉讼的话\N{\fs12}if you want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然后那房子就是我的了\N{\fs12}And then the house is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那我可以搬回去和唐尼一起住了吗\N{\fs12}I could move back there with Donnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那幢房子\N{\fs12}Well, not that house,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是哈西会支付你土地的钱  然后你就可以买房子了\N{\fs12}but Hassey would pay you for the land and then you could buy a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,给我和唐尼\N{\fs12}For me and Donnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我想如果你的健康状况得到改善\N{\fs12}Well, I think if your health improves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼可能会和你一起生活\N{\fs12}there's a chance that Donnie could live with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,机会有多大\N{\fs12}How good a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那我不太清楚\N{\fs12}Well, that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那我想要打官司  可以吗\N{\fs12}I want to fight. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,露露提出了对哈西宣告判决的动议\N{\fs12}Lulu filed a motion for declaratory judgment against Hassey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你会和她谈谈\N{\fs12}I thought you were gonna talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我会的\N{\fs12}Well, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我试过了\N{\fs12}Well... I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在跟进那个孩子的事  所以我想我不能参与这个案子了\N{\fs12}Well, I'm still working with that kid, so I guess I'm off the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  还有你和对方律师上床的事\N{\fs12}Yeah. That and the fact that you're sleeping with opposing counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我想说  我想说你不需要参与这个案子了\N{\fs12}Yeah, I'd say-- I'd say you're off the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉哈西的\N{\fs12}I'll tell Hassey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  露露\N{\fs12}Hey, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  你在这里做什么\N{\fs12}Burton. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  给你委托人一万美元怎么样\N{\fs12}Well, how does $10,000 to your client sound
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他立即放弃财产索赔\N{\fs12}if he drops his property claim immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一万美元  - 是的\N{\fs12}- $10,000? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  你不能用令人厌恶的钱来收买我的客户\N{\fs12}Burton, you can't buy my client off with a nuisance value.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌吗  在我的家乡  一万美元是一大笔钱啊\N{\fs12}Nuisance? Where I come from, $10,000 is a lot of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是当一个人运气不好的时候\N{\fs12}especially when a man's down on his luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我客户的索赔值六位数  而不是五位数\N{\fs12}My client's claim is worth mid-six figures, not low fives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我来问你个问题\N{\fs12}Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前处理过逆权占有申索吗\N{\fs12}You ever handle a adverse possession claim before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白这有什么关系\N{\fs12}I don't see how that's relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我处理过  相信我\N{\fs12}I have, and believe me--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗什么  我肯定能处理好的\N{\fs12}You know what? I'm sure I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你可以的\N{\fs12}Oh, I'm sure you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想确认一下你们是否能接受一个合适的报价\N{\fs12}I'd just like to make sure that you recognize a good offer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当它呈现给你的时候\N{\fs12}when it's presented to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我可以  我只是不认为这是合理的报价\N{\fs12}Oh, I can. I just don't think this is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你把我告上法庭  但你输了\N{\fs12}lf you take me to court and you lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得得向你提出制裁和法律费用\N{\fs12}I'm gonna have to hit you with sanctions and legal costs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我也就不确定这个地方还能不能撑得下去\N{\fs12}and I'm not real sure this place could afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在威胁我吗  伯顿\N{\fs12}Are you threatening me, Burton?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不  并不是的\N{\fs12}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想让你想一想  仅此而已\N{\fs12}I just want you to think about it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经考虑过了\N{\fs12}I have thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的提议被否决了\N{\fs12}Your offer's rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧   保重\N{\fs12}Okay. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚在LSP那边\N{\fs12}I was just over at LSP.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs12}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  路易莎\N{\fs12}Uh, Louisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那边儿也做不了什么了  孩子\N{\fs12}You got your hands full there, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道\N{\fs12}Right. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她对这个财产索赔很认真\N{\fs12}She's serious about this claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哈西每天都坐在那块土地上\N{\fs12}And every day that Hassey sits on that property,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这花了他几千美元\N{\fs12}it costs him thousands of dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  她只是在做她认为最好的事\N{\fs12}Well, she's just doing what she thinks is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  如果她继续这样做的话\N{\fs12}You know, if she moves forward with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要像对待其他对手一样对待她\N{\fs12}I'm gonna have to treat her like any other adversary.
