Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这种行为是没有意义的\N{\fs12}I'm gonna claim the action is frivolous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要求LSP支付所有的法律成本和损失的收入\N{\fs12}and demand LSP pay for all the legal costs and lost revenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  不管怎么说  这个家伙  拉尔夫·隆戈\N{\fs12}Well, for what it's worth, this guy, Ralph Longo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要的只是一个居住的地方\N{\fs12}all he needs is a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  罗恩  - 伯顿\N{\fs12}- Hey, Ron. - Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗  - 好吧  我们拭目以待\N{\fs12}- How you doing? - Well, we'll see.
