Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,罗恩  恐怕我儿子不能参与这个案子了\N{\fs12}Ron, I'm afraid my son has got to step away from the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你觉得怎么好  就怎么办\N{\fs12}Well, whatever you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs12}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我和隆戈的律师谈了谈  她拒绝了我们的提议\N{\fs12}So I talked to Longo's attorney, and she turned down our offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他拒绝了一万美元\N{\fs12}He turned down ten grand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  什么样的流浪汉会拒绝一万美元\N{\fs12}Burton, what kind of homeless guy turns down ten grand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我把钱都花在这件事上了\N{\fs12}I am hemorrhaging money on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  但是我们还有其他的选择\N{\fs12}I know that, but we do have other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 比如说  - 好吧  我们可以起诉\N{\fs12}- Like what? - Well, we could fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那只会花费很多的钱  浪费很多的时间\N{\fs12}That's just gonna cost a lot of money, waste a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我们可以再报一次价\N{\fs12}Or we could make a different offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 更多的钱  - 不行\N{\fs12}- Of more money? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙想要的只是一个家  和  呃\N{\fs12}All this guy wants is a home, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而你碰巧有几千个公寓  所以\N{\fs12}and you happen to have several thousand, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我给这个家伙一个吗\N{\fs12}You want me to give this guy one of my units?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要太好的  但我想这样就行了\N{\fs12}It doesn't have to be fancy, but I think that might do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样所有的麻烦都可以解决了吗\N{\fs12}And that would make this whole mess go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是那么认为的\N{\fs12}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,做生意的另一个成本\N{\fs12}Another cost of doing business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们解决它吧\N{\fs12}Let's just get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  罗恩  我会随时通知你的\N{\fs12}Okay, Ron. I'll keep you posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴见到你  - 我也是\N{\fs12}- Good to see you. - You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  我要早点回家  我觉得不太舒服\N{\fs12}Hey, I'm gonna go home a little early. I'm not feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 我很抱歉\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  你的活我可以替你做\N{\fs12}No, I can cover for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢你\N{\fs12}All right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你怀孕多长时间了\N{\fs12}How far along are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  只有六个星期\N{\fs12}Uh, just six weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克的吗\N{\fs12}Nick's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是的\N{\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我认为这很好\N{\fs12}Well, I think that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你会成为一个好妈妈的\N{\fs12}You're gonna be a wonderful mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  呃  你有什么计划\N{\fs12}So, uh, what are your plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,关于工作  你的工作计划\N{\fs12}About work. Work plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往地  只是  你知道的  工作\N{\fs12}Same as always, just... you know, to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 为什么这么问\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  如果你想休产假\N{\fs12}Well, if you want to take maternity leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  对啊\N{\fs12}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里  你知道的  可以做任何事\N{\fs12}I'm here, you know, to do whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢你\N{\fs12}Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的是  给我一些忠告\N{\fs12}All I'm saying is, you know, give me some warning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我已经习惯了自由\N{\fs12}because I've kinda gotten used to the free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算竞选市议会议员\N{\fs12}I'm planning to run for City Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道  随便什么\N{\fs12}But, you know...whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要我跟董事谈一谈  或者是放松一下\N{\fs12}lf you need me to talk to the Board or take the reins back for awhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我\N{\fs12}just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算呆在这儿  阿尔文\N{\fs12}Well, I'm planning on staying here, Alvin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,长期的  你知道的  所以\N{\fs12}for the long term, you know? So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是说你会离开  露露\N{\fs12}I'm not suggesting you weren't, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你感到高兴  露露\N{\fs12}I'm happy for you, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你和尼克  真的很高兴\N{\fs12}You and Nick. Truly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你爸爸  呃  有一点盛气凌人\N{\fs12}So, today your dad was, uh, a little condescending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他问我以前是否处理过这样的索赔\N{\fs12}Yeah, he asked me if I ever handled a claim like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那你处理过呢\N{\fs12}Well, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是重点\N{\fs12}That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉你我们的谈话了吗\N{\fs12}Did he tell you about our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他去找你了\N{\fs12}He said that he went to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他我们的事了吗\N{\fs12}Did you tell him about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怀孕的事吗  不  没有告诉他\N{\fs12}About the pregnancy? No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那求婚的事儿呢\N{\fs12}What about the proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你知道  我  呃\N{\fs12}Well, you know, l, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实向他要了我妈妈的戒指\N{\fs12}I did ask him for my mother's ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你妈妈的戒指\N{\fs12}That was your mother's ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没告诉过我这个  - 没关系的\N{\fs12}- You didn't tell me that. - It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你爸爸会讨厌我吗\N{\fs12}Do you think maybe your dad resents me being--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这只是他做生意的方式\N{\fs12}No, it's just the way he does business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fs12}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你得让我离开那个基督教的收容所\N{\fs12}You gotta get me out of that Christian men's shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 鲁弗斯  - 你得让我离开那里\N{\fs12}- Rufus. - You gotta get me out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方就像个监狱  一群动物在里面\N{\fs12}lt's like a prison in that place, bunch a animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没问过你爸是怎么死的\N{\fs12}You know, I never asked how your dad died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抽烟\N{\fs12}Smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,酗酒\N{\fs12}Drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也和你爸爸一起喝过酒\N{\fs12}I used to drink with your dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候晚上在码头上  然后  呃\N{\fs12}down on the dock some nights and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计  他真的是很能喝\N{\fs12}Man, he could really put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也和他一起打球  你知道吗\N{\fs12}But I played ball with him, too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  他打球  而我坐冷板凳\N{\fs12}I mean, he played and I rode the pine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一场对阵辛雷的比赛  双加时赛\N{\fs12}But there was this one game against Schenley, double overtime.
