Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,无论辛雷做什么  他们都无法阻止鲍比\N{\fs12}And no matter what Schenley did, they couldn't stop Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:23:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我过去常和他在车道上玩篮球\N{\fs12}I used to play hoops with him in the driveway.
