Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他另一只手里总是拿着啤酒瓶\N{\fs12}because he always had a beer bottle in the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我想了很多\N{\fs12}Alvin, I've been thinking a lot.
