Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文·马斯特森  听着  有一位先生和我在一起\N{\fs12}Alvin Masterson. Listen, I have a gentleman here with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他正在处理一些问题  但是\N{\fs12}who has some issues he's working on but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他在休利特公寓可能会成功\N{\fs12}I think that he may succeed at Hewlett House.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我可以等\N{\fs12}Yeah, I can hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,唷\N{\fs12}Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果隆戈先生放弃这一不利占有要求\N{\fs12}lf Mr. Longo will drop this adverse possession claim,
