Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.18,0:24:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的委托人最终什么也得不到\N{\fs12}your client's gonna end up receiving nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.35,0:24:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你会浪费很多宝贵的时间\N{\fs12}And you're gonna be wasting a lot of your valuable time
