Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.92,0:32:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  他总是说如果他有一个孙子  他肯定会像我一样\N{\fs12}Well, he always said if he had a grandson, he'd bet he'd be like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.37,0:32:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经开玩笑地叫过他祖父  他很喜欢\N{\fs12}I called him Gramps once as a joke and he liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.48,0:32:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们什么时候认识的\N{\fs12}When did you two hook up?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.22,0:32:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,四年前我刚到匹兹堡的时候\N{\fs12}Four years ago when I first got to Pittsburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.55,0:32:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫看到我被一些年龄较大的孩子欺负了\N{\fs12}Ralph saw me getting my ass kicked by some older kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.40,0:32:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他赶走了他们  所以\N{\fs12}and he chased them off, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.41,0:32:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我被打得很惨  他说我可以留下来\N{\fs12}I was pretty beat-up, and he said I could stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.61,0:32:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他从来没有让我离开\N{\fs12}He never asked me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.43,0:32:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫知道你在他家里卖毒品吗\N{\fs12}Did Ralph know you were selling drugs out of his house?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.34,0:32:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不知道\N{\fs12}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.88,0:32:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是实话吗\N{\fs12}You telling me the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.28,0:32:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他知道  他会杀了我\N{\fs12}He'd kill me if he knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.73,0:32:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不得不赚钱\N{\fs12}But I had to to make some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.68,0:32:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫无法工作\N{\fs12}Ralph couldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.28,0:32:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不和他在一起  他撑不了一年的\N{\fs12}lf I'm not with him, he won't last a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.68,0:32:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我进监狱的话  他会怎么样\N{\fs12}What's gonna happen to him if I go to jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.43,0:33:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来照顾他\N{\fs12}Who's gonna take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.65,0:33:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在对他的刑事指控尚未处理之前\N{\fs12}Pending disposition of the criminal charges against him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.55,0:33:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,唐纳德·门德斯的监护权要立刻回到他母亲手上\N{\fs12}Donald Mendez is to be returned immediately to his mother's custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.57,0:33:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,唐尼\N{\fs12}Donnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.74,0:33:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未停止过祈祷  我从未停止过\N{\fs12}I never stopped praying. I never stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.19,0:33:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要带唐尼去哪里\N{\fs12}Where are they taking Donnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.92,0:33:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他的公设辩护人提出了申辩\N{\fs12}His public defender worked out a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.86,0:33:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他将在韦恩堡服缓刑\N{\fs12}He's gonna be serving his probation in Fort Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.48,0:33:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们要把他带到哪里去\N{\fs12}But where are they taking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.79,0:33:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他要回印第安纳州与他的妈妈住在一起\N{\fs12}He's going back to Indiana to live with his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.64,0:33:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  我带你回医院\N{\fs12}Come on. I'm going to take you back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.14,0:33:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我他没有家人了\N{\fs12}He told me he had no family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.80,0:33:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他一直都在流浪\N{\fs12}He said he was living on the street his whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.95,0:34:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,休利特公寓今天早上打电话给我了\N{\fs12}Hewlett House called me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.39,0:34:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我赶出去了  你得给我找一个新地方了\N{\fs12}They threw me out. You got to find me a new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.01,0:34:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发现你在吸毒\N{\fs12}They found you doing meth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.84,0:34:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.15,0:34:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过你会保持清白的\N{\fs12}You said you were gonna stay clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.66,0:34:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别提了  伙计  我们都不干净\N{\fs12}Come on, man! None of us are clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.31,0:34:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得超级流浪汉是干净的吗  他现在很兴奋\N{\fs12}You think Super Bum is clean? He's high right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.38,0:34:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,得了  别那么惊讶\N{\fs12}Come on now! Don't look so so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你的电梯里买了冰毒\N{\fs12}I bought the meth on your elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.14,0:34:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从我身边的一个孩子那里\N{\fs12}from one of the kids that lives on the lot from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.06,0:34:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看  阿尔文  我搞砸了\N{\fs12}Look, Alvin, I slipped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,给休利特公司打电话吧  再给我一次机会\N{\fs12}Just call Hewlett House. Give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.06,0:34:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你老爸会帮助我的\N{\fs12}Your old man would have helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.97,0:34:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次  我在酒吧后面晕了过去\N{\fs12}This one time, I passed out behind the bar
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.14,0:34:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有两个家伙想把我打翻\N{\fs12}and these two guys tried to roll me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.87,0:34:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后鲍比出来了\N{\fs12}and Bobby comes out of--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.70,0:34:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天去了奥尔德里奇高中\N{\fs12}I went to Aldrich High School yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.85,0:34:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲从没有在高中打过球\N{\fs12}My dad never played senior year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.61,0:34:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他从来没有做过校队\N{\fs12}He never even made varsity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.23,0:34:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我参加了一个新赛季的比赛\N{\fs12}I Half a season freshman ball that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.99,0:34:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  你打了\N{\fs12}You played, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.64,0:34:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,队长  赛季的最有价值球员\N{\fs12}Team captain. Season MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.56,0:34:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你打了两场加时赛\N{\fs12}You played that double-overtime game.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.64,0:35:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  听着\N{\fs12}Hey, look--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.40,0:35:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你也替那孩子挨打了吗\N{\fs12}Did you take the paddling for that kid, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.42,0:35:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  是我被打了\N{\fs12}Yeah, I'm the one that got paddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.84,0:35:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,离开我的办公室\N{\fs12}Just get out of my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.96,0:35:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉了你  你想听的\N{\fs12}I told you what I thought you wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.07,0:35:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  休利特公寓现在是不可能了\N{\fs12}Well, Hewlett House is out of the question now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.09,0:35:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去别的地方吧\N{\fs12}Well, someplace else then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.75,0:35:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去打几个电话\N{\fs12}I'll make a few calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.19,0:35:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.65,0:35:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在月底有一个募捐活动\N{\fs12}We have a fundraiser scheduled for the end of the month,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.61,0:35:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,并打电话让你进入匹兹堡政坛\N{\fs12}and I made some calls to get you onto Pittsburgh politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.62,0:35:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你拒绝了\N{\fs12}I thought you were Ieaning towards no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.57,0:35:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是拒绝了  但我想了想你说的话\N{\fs12}I was. But then I thought about what you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.10,0:35:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,关于你的经历  你和穷人的合作\N{\fs12}about your experience, your work with the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.05,0:35:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你有良好的意愿  阿尔文\N{\fs12}You got good intensions, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.52,0:35:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很美好  没有其他的了\N{\fs12}lt's sweet, nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.92,0:36:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.71,0:36:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我得走了\N{\fs12}Well, gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.18,0:36:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我稍后会打电话给你  讨论安排一些辩论\N{\fs12}I'll call you later to talk about setting up some debates.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.42,0:36:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.50,0:36:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs12}What's that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.63,0:36:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一个改变的机会  小罗伯特\N{\fs12}An opportunity for change, young Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.35,0:36:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一个改变的机会\N{\fs12}An opportunity of a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.00,0:36:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,唐尼的妈妈开车送他回家的途中\N{\fs12}Donnie's mother was driving him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.60,0:36:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在第一次红灯时  他跳了出来  来到了这里\N{\fs12}At the first red light, he jumps out and comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.62,0:36:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事\N{\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.64,0:36:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想和拉尔夫一起走  但他们甚至没能穿过走廊\N{\fs12}He tried to leave with Ralph, but they didn't even make it down the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.85,0:36:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 唐尼在哪儿  - 他在这里\N{\fs12}- Where's Donnie? - He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.23,0:36:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,唐尼\N{\fs12}Donnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.65,0:36:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  什么\N{\fs12}What--what.. .
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.60,0:36:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他会怎么样\N{\fs12}What's gonna happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.46,0:36:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他的缓刑将被撤销\N{\fs12}His probation will be revoked,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.90,0:36:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他将因持有毒品而服刑\N{\fs12}and he'll have to serve the sentence for drug possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.91,0:36:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果它们是我的毒品呢  - 隆戈先生\N{\fs12}- What if they were my drugs? - Mr. Longo--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.96,0:36:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果毒品是我的  唐尼就不会进监狱了\N{\fs12}Donnie can't go to prison for drugs if they were mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.01,0:36:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他卖毒品是为了我  这样我们就有钱了\N{\fs12}He was selling them for me so we'd have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.86,0:36:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是很严重的  隆戈先生\N{\fs12}What you're saying is very serious, Mr. Longo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.66,0:36:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请你给我一点时间好吗\N{\fs12}Will you give me a minute, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.32,0:36:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我知道你是想帮忙  但你只会把事情弄得更糟\N{\fs12}Listen, I know you're trying to help, but you're just gonna make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.33,0:36:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  安静点  好吗  请给我一点时间\N{\fs12}Please, just be quiet, okay? Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.20,0:37:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他不是那个意思\N{\fs12}You know he didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.53,0:37:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是你有道德义务\N{\fs12}What I mean is that you have an ethical obligation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.15,0:37:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对他说的话保密\N{\fs12}to keep what he said to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.53,0:37:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 因为这是机密信息\N{\fs12}Why? - Because it's privileged information.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.31,0:37:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫不是我的委托人\N{\fs12}Ralph isn't my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.36,0:37:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你为LSP工作  他是LSP的委托人  他是你的委托人\N{\fs12}You work for LSP. He's an LSP client. He's your client.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.44,0:37:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  别这样  露露  你听到了  我也听到了\N{\fs12}Oh, come on, Lulu. You heard it. I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.25,0:37:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他公开承认使用这片地产是为了犯罪\N{\fs12}He publicly admitted to using that property for criminal purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.51,0:37:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这就否定了他的逆权占有要求\N{\fs12}That kills his adverse possession claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.40,0:37:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是一个保护他所爱男孩的老人\N{\fs12}He's just an old man who's protecting a boy that he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.09,0:37:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样  尼克\N{\fs12}Come on, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.72,0:37:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  它是保密的\N{\fs12}Besides, it's privileged.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.46,0:37:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.58,0:37:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你说服了客户  这是一笔好的交易\N{\fs12}Well, I'm glad you convinced your client this is a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.35,0:37:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯  有道理  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Well, it made sense. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.11,0:37:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我来起草公寓的文件\N{\fs12}I'll draw up the papers for the apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.84,0:37:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下个星期  我会寄给你一张1万美元的支票  好吗\N{\fs12}and then next week, I'll send you a cashier's check for $10,000, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.06,0:38:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  谢谢  - 你说对了  谢谢\N{\fs12}- Okay. Thank you. - You bet. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.56,0:38:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.69,0:38:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我在办公室还有一些工作要完成  我们在家见面\N{\fs12}Uh, I have some work to finish up at the office. I'll see you at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.48,0:38:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.50,0:38:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见  - 再见  保重\N{\fs12}- Bye. - Bye. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.89,0:38:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟她谈过这件事吗\N{\fs12}Did you talk to her about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.90,0:38:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.44,0:38:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她就这样改变主意了\N{\fs12}She just changed her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.20,0:38:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我想是的\N{\fs12}Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.31,0:38:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这对哈西来说是个好买卖\N{\fs12}This is a good deal for Hassey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.81,0:38:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道  那位年轻女士打赢了案子\N{\fs12}Truth be known, that young lady had a winning case.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.59,0:38:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我知道\N{\fs12}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.16,0:38:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  那纳马柯林呢  我们还去吗\N{\fs12}Hey, what about Namacolin? Are we still on?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.95,0:38:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.20,0:38:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你会带露露来吗\N{\fs12}Are you gonna bring Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.78,0:38:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你问过她吗\N{\fs12}Have you even asked her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.26,0:38:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没抽出时间来\N{\fs12}I haven't gotten around to it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.76,0:38:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  问她  带她过来  好吗\N{\fs12}Nicholas, ask her. Bring her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.63,0:38:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对你有好处  好吗\N{\fs12}lt'll be good for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.69,0:39:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.03,0:39:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚跟劳里谈了谈\N{\fs12}I just spoke to Laurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.69,0:39:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她将在明天开设唐尼的犯罪听证会\N{\fs12}She's gonna set up Donnie's delinquency hearing for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.84,0:39:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  她已经打电话给我了\N{\fs12}Yeah, she already called.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.17,0:39:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想唐尼的妈妈\N{\fs12}You know, I can't stop thinking about Donnie's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.21,0:39:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  当你的儿子还是个小男孩的时候\N{\fs12}I mean, you lose your son when he's a little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.67,0:39:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你花了很多年寻找他  想知道他是否还活着\N{\fs12}you spend years looking for him, wondering if he's even alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.23,0:39:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然后有一天  突然  电话响了\N{\fs12}And then one day, out of the blue, the phone rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.82,0:39:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当她看到他的时候\N{\fs12}And when she sees him, I mean, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.74,0:39:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他不再是个孩子了  他是个男人了\N{\fs12}\N{\fs12}he's not a kid anymore, he's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.20,0:39:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不再像她丢失的那个男孩\N{\fs12}Couldn't possibly resemble the boy she lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.67,0:39:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在她又要失去他了\N{\fs12}And now she's gonna lose him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.39,0:39:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,许多父母辜负了他们的孩子\N{\fs12}So many parents fail their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.52,0:39:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.43,0:39:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,做错误的决定似乎很容易\N{\fs12}It just seems so easy to make all the wrong decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.69,0:39:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我想你只要尽力就行了\N{\fs12}Well, I guess you just got to do the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.59,0:39:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.00,0:40:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.72,0:40:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是在这里看到了错误的决定\N{\fs12}You only ever see the wrong decisions here.
